Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:14.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何ページも費やして　つづられた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:21.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうしてか一行の　空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:30.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}押花のしおりはさんで　君と転がす使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:37.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れかけのレンガを　積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:42.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}海を見渡す坂を駆けのぼって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:47.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:55.19,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君をさがしている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうやって今は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:09.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ二人はすぐそこに居るのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:15.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうかまた会えますように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:25.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なんて　どうかしてるみたい
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------OPCN------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:14.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}使用好几页 填补了我们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:21.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却弥补不了那唯一的一行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:30.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夹上干花书签 和你乘上骑一次就扔的自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:37.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往用几乎遗忘的砖头堆积起来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:42.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}爬上望得见海的小坡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:47.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}头上是湛蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:55.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}右手是碳酸饮料 左手一直在寻求着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:02.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在呢 你也不会再追问我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:09.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两个人明明还在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:15.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}而我却祈愿能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:25.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可能是我的错觉吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------EDJP------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}出会いは　ふっとした　瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:39.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:44.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}声をかけてくれたね「一緒に帰ろう」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:51.50,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}あぁ　花火が夜空　きれいに咲いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.65,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}ちょっとセツナク
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:22:00.32,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}あぁ　風が時間とともに　流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:07.73,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}嬉しくって　楽しくって　冒険も　いろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:14.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}二人の　秘密の　基地の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:18.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君と夏の終わり　将来の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}大きな希望を忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:29.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}10年後の8月　また出会えるのを　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:31.05,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君が最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:36.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}心から「ありがとう」叫んでたこと　知ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}涙をこらえて　笑顔でさようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:43.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}せつないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:52.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be5}最高の思い出を…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------EDCN------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}邂逅是瞬间的巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:39.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在回家的路口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:44.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}你对我说「一起回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:51.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}啊 烟花在夜空里绚丽地绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}有些伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:22:00.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}啊 风随着时间一起流动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:07.73,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}开心的 愉快的冒险也经历过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:14.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在两个人的秘密基地里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:18.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}不会忘记和你度过的夏天 将来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}和巨大的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:29.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}相信着十年后的八月还能与你再会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:31.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我知道你自始至终
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:36.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}都在心里喊「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}强忍泪水 笑着说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:43.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}有些伤感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:52.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be5}怀着最美好的回忆
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请实现我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就成了还魂似的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了  芽间为了实现愿望而还魂回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得这只是我看到的幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想？也就是fantasy？  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在也在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间是我啊  在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里  芽间  露个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然趁势就把芽间的事说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这些他能这么乖乖的接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  我看不见她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这只是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太果然太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘密基地你在用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在日本的时候用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  那些红色的标记就是去过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看世界上各种各样的地方呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用打工挣的钱去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:02:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有时间去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵子去了东南亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  越南的姑娘真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太真强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那么小的个子  现在长这么壮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？  变了不少哦  Jungle Cruise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑题了跑题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间的请求是吧  有过什么约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  记不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是曾说过想要仁太的「是的哦」的签名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是的哦」哪至于变鬼还要来取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的栗丸怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去后给你吃酸奶哦酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子你真的去了宿海家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去照顾家里蹲真是倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是偶尔不是有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么没精神 早上很辛苦什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也偶尔会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦  但我不想被视为那阴沉的家伙的同类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在绝对在拿鸣子想色色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王大附属的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤…鹤见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就不要管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和绿高的女生说话的情形要是被谁看见的话太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思  等下！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好心给你送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}你什么时候这么高傲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣  鹤子  不能吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}以前明明那么低调
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就容易被别人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和刚才你身边那些轻浮的女人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻浮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明一直在模仿本间芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死人的名字别随便挂在嘴边！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出自自己之口让自己痛苦  真没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想变得和芽间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  仁太是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢芽间的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我没有那样挑动他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…  谁会喜欢这丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等仁太  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而后…变成了那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙在叫了就~回~家了  青蛙在叫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…应该回哪里去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要找什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  布袋妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人要买你有意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布袋妖怪哪一作  蛋白石？  绿宝石？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？布袋妖怪金  那是哪一年出的老古董了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之有卖的话就赶紧拿出来  赶紧卖给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  稀有布袋怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  芽间超想要的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直没能入手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像说过Bilbilder什么的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就决定这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4571日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前出的游戏定价卖是不是太黑了点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先申明了 这可是良心价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个已经绝版了  定价卖算便宜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事！谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来仁太君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天刚好从现场弄回来了很不错的盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吃烤肉大餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  没食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这算什么真不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么玩来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始三只里面选一只…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力具现化的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不该存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你…仁太
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗…  久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前那样叫噗噗就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热情点嘛  阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这叫法是第一次听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  对了雪集知道吗  仁太身边芽间还魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…宿海怎么说芽间的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太他呢  好久不见了还是一如既往那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海怎么说芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻听？还是幻想来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太懂  芽间好像说什么请实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间你回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫洗什么澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸也在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  总觉得洗澡除了凉飕飕外别无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间讨厌这样  仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀  对成长后的自己稍微注意一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然某部分还没怎么成长的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这少年好像哪里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好！好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  难道是噗噗？  好高！成长期真可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友交换？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  用连接线交换布袋妖怪后就可以获得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大叔  肉好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是昨晚的剩菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大叔我去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也说了「要大家一起才能实现」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害噗噗  怎么想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说我也看见幻听了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻听不是看的是听的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样啊  那再买一个布袋妖怪的游戏卡就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  有布袋妖怪的人其他还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好可爱呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候最讨厌自己的卷发和眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔顺长发的芽间…被仁太喜爱的芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣  贴纸贴成成对的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给安鸣一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢芽间…却也很讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子  有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  连我也要玩布袋妖怪？开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系偶尔一玩  回归童心  是吧仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  眼镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你俩来家里还真是怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚鸣子做的果冻吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣的果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再叫这名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之稀有布袋妖怪可是芽间的愿望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋别说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没…  芽间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  在梦中出现了还是该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布袋妖怪在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  那是Love&Perry的卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是牛王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  牛王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直不过来这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为芽间在的话妈妈和安鸣都会变得伤心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bo☆bobo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这么个小游戏上还贴名字…你真是规矩的人呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔了好久重新看bo☆bobo真是有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌不能相信  为什么没有波伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为稀有布袋妖怪不是要把波伊扎和钢格尔交换…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领域内没有波伊扎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得让波伊特进化  我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣果然没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对大家很好  还有很多游戏漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种气氛总觉得好久不见了  真开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了  波伊扎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了  安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么  就当打发时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你的报酬有么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来上学哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来把连接线接上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了这样就可以和朋友交换了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布袋妖怪到手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  这下芽间也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望好像不是这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好事有许多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太安鸣还有噗噗又成了好朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不当自己事啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心摔倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没~关~系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间最近全是快乐事~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的说哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间最近全是快乐事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许久没这么快乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的精神创伤虽然还没有消失的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然有明天的话  道歉就算慢慢来也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始这样想了
